name: PRAYAS KENDRA SANSTHA HARSOLI

address: Village and Post - Harsoli, Via Dudu,

briefDescription: Prayas Kendra Sanstha Harsoli is a voluntary organisation registered under the Rajasthan Societies Act, 1958. Prayas Kendra is working towards building a justifiable and sustainable society so that every poor community gets benefited from the development process. The organisation is working mainly with Dalits in the areas of Land and water conservation, Environment conservation, Women Welfare, Health improvement, Improving livelihood etc.
